snippet: Emirates Team New Zealand led the entire way in the first real race of the America’s Cup challenger series. Italy’s Luna Rossa boycotted Sunday’s opening race.
abstract: Emirates Team New Zealand leads the entire way and routes Italy’s Luna Rossa in the first real race of the America’s Cup challenger series on San Francisco Bay.
lead_paragraph: Emirates Team New Zealand led the entire way in the first real race of the America’s Cup challenger series. Italy’s Luna Rossa boycotted Sunday’s opening race.

headline.main: New Zealand Wins First Real Race of America’s Cup Challenger Series
